ox; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Norasmiy mehnat orqali yashab, oilasini boqayotganlar ko&lsquo;pincha jiddiy ijtimoiy maummolarga duch keladi. Xalqaro mehnat tashkilotining (XMT) so&lsquo;nggi hisobotiga ko&lsquo;ra, bugun norasmiy iqtisodiyotda 2 milliard odam ishlamoqda. Jahonda ish bilan band aholining 60 foizdan ortig&lsquo;i norasmiy mehnat bilan band.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Norasmiy bandlik dunyoning barcha mamlakatlarida mavjud. Uning darajasi har bir mamlakatning ijtimoiy &ndash; iqtisodiy salohiyati, amalga oshirilayotgan islohotlarning ustuvor yo&lsquo;nalishlariga bevosita bog&lsquo;liq.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shimoliy va Janubiy Amerikada norasmiy bandlik darajasi 40 foiz bo&lsquo;lsa, Janubiy Osiyodagi ayrim mamlakatlarda 80 foizgacha yetadi. Afrikada norasmiy bandlik ulushi 86 foizni tashkil qiladi. Yevropa va Markaziy Osiyo mintaqasida bu ko&lsquo;rsatkich 25,0 foiz, arab mamlakatlarida qariyib - 70,0 foizni tashkil etadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Mamlakatimizda yashirin iqtisodiyot ko&lsquo;lamini aniqlash va uni qisqartirishga qaratilgan chora-tadbirlar amalga oshirilmoqda. 2024-yilning 16-yanvar kuni O&lsquo;zbekiston Prezidenti raisligida makroiqtisodiy barqarorlik va iqtisodiy rivojlanishni ta&rsquo;minlash bo&lsquo;yicha ustuvor vazifalar yuzasidan o&lsquo;tkazilgan videoselektor yig&lsquo;ilishida ham yashirin iqtisodiyot muammosi bugungi kunda eng dolzarb masala ekanligi qayd etildi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Rasmiy statistik ma&rsquo;lumotlarga ko&lsquo;ra, 2024-yilning 1-yanvar holatiga ko&lsquo;ra, O&lsquo;zbekistonda jami band aholining 39,0 foizi norasmiy sektorda faoliyat ko&lsquo;rsatmoqda. Mamlakatda 5,5 millionga yaqin kishi norasmiy sektorda mehnat qilayapti.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;nggi yillarda O&lsquo;zbekistonda mehnatga layoqatli aholining norasmiy sektorda bandligi ma&rsquo;lum darajada pasaydi (2020-yil &ndash; 42,8 foiz, 2023-yil &ndash; 39,0 foiz), ya&rsquo;ni norasmiy bandlik oxirgi 4 yilda 3,8 foizga yoki 0,2 mln. kishiga kamaygan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Buning asosiy sabablaridan biri o&lsquo;zini &ndash; o&lsquo;zi band qilishning davlat tomonidan qo&lsquo;llab-quvvatlanishidir. Shuningdek, ishsizlik darajasining 2020-2023 yillarda (3,7 foiz punktiga) kamayishi bilan norasmiy bandlik o&lsquo;rtasida bevosita bog&lsquo;liqlikni kuzatish mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Kuzatuv natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, mamlakat hududlarida norasmiy bandlik darajasida ma&rsquo;lum tafovutlar mavjud. Norasmiy bandlikning eng yuqori darajasi Namangan (50 foiz), Surxondaryo va Jizzax (49 foiz), Qashqadaryo (48,4 foiz) viloyatlariga to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladi. Eng past ko&lsquo;rsatkich esa Toshkent shahri (10,9 foiz) va Navoiy (21,8 foiz) viloyatiga va nisbatan past ko&lsquo;rsatkich Buxoro (32,3 foiz) va Toshkent (34,9 foiz) viloyatlarida kuzatildi. Hududlar o&lsquo;rtasidagi farq Toshkent shahridan tashqari 2,3 martani tashkil qilgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Iqtisodiyotning norasmiy sektorida band bo&lsquo;lganlar soni asosan vaqtinchalik, bir martalik va mavsumiy ishlarni bajaruvchilar (94,4 ming kishi) hamda yuridik shaxs maqomiga ega bo&lsquo;lmagan dehqon xo&lsquo;jaliklarida norasmiy band bo&lsquo;lganlar sonining (141,2 ming kishi) keskin qisqarishi hisobiga kamaygan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Norasmiy bandlikning kamayishida ma&rsquo;lum ijobiy o&lsquo;zgarishlar kuzatilayotgan bo&lsquo;lsada, hal etilishini kutayotgan muammolar ham saqlanib qolmoqda.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Keyingi yillarda yashirin iqtisodiyot ko&lsquo;lamini keskin qisqartirish orqali mamlakatda sog&lsquo;lom raqobat va xususiy biznesni rivojlantirish choralari ko&lsquo;rilayotir. Xususan, &laquo;O&lsquo;zbekiston - 2030&raquo; strategiyasida yashirin iqtisodiyotni qisqartirish orqali soliq bazasini qo&lsquo;shimcha kengaytirish imkoniyatidan foydalanish o&lsquo;z ifodasini topgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shuningdek, mazkur strategiyada bandlik ko&lsquo;lamini oshirish va munosib mehnat sharoitlarini yaratish orqali mehnat bozorining barqarorligini ta&rsquo;minlashga alohida e&rsquo;tibor qaratilgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Norasmiy bandlikni tartibga solishga qaratilgan chora-tadbirlar:</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><a name="_Hlk162514260" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"></a><a name="_Hlk162514239" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">- ishlab chiqarish, xizmatlar sohasini, oilaviy biznesni va kasanachilikni yanada rivojlantirish uchun mahalla salohiyatidan foydalangan holda norasmiy tadbirkorlarni ro&lsquo;yxatga olish (rasmiy band qilish) mexanizmini takomillashtirish;</a></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- mahallalarda norasmiy band bo&lsquo;lgan aholi o&lsquo;rtasida so&lsquo;rov o&lsquo;tkazish, norasmiy bandlik ulushini qisqartirish, mehnat resurslari balansini zamonaviy yondashuvlar asosida shakllantirish;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- mahallalarda mavjud bo&lsquo;lgan norasmiy xizmat ko&lsquo;rsatishni rasmiylashtirish maqsadga muvofiq.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Botir Abdullayev,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">MHTI loyiha rahbari</strong></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;">286</span></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; fon